claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table presenting demographic characteristics of study participants across four groups (n=122, 120, 283, 198), including mean age, age groups, sex, race/ethnicity, study sites, and prior influenza vaccination history. The table contains only participant demographics and vaccination history and provides no data on antigenic match with WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains, and thus does not support the claim.
